---
layout: layout.njk
title: Blog
permalink: blog/index.html
description: Writing on distributed systems, engineering practice, and related topics.
---
<section class="section wrap blog-hero" aria-labelledby="blog-heading">
  <p class="eyebrow">Writing</p>
  <h1 id="blog-heading" class="section-title blog-index-title">Blog</h1>
  <p class="prose blog-intro">
    Occasional notes for recruiters and peers — architecture, operability, and
    lessons from large-scale systems. Subscribe via
    <a href="{{ page.url | rootRel }}feed.xml">Atom feed</a>.
  </p>

  <ol class="post-list" role="list">
    {% for post in collections.postsSorted %}
      <li>
        <article class="post-list-item">
          <time class="post-list-date" datetime="{{ post.date | dateIso }}"
            >{{ post.date | readableDate }}</time
          >
          <h2 class="post-list-title">
            <a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a>
          </h2>
          {% if post.data.description %}
            <p class="post-list-excerpt">{{ post.data.description }}</p>
          {% endif %}
        </article>
      </li>
    {% endfor %}
  </ol>

  {% if (collections.postsSorted | length) === 0 %}
    <p class="prose">No posts yet — check back soon.</p>
  {% endif %}
</section>
